<br>
I have more or less decided to go for a Thief or Scout type class, and was just wondering about opinions on the various options ..<br>
<br>
Initial choice was to go for a  Saracen Infiltrator .. but apparently they are a little weak at the moment, however I do like the idea of sneaking into enemy keeps at later levels.<br>
<br>
Then i was reading about Archer classes who are supposedly very useful in RvR but weaker in PvE. As such, I was wondering how common are RvR encounters? Is that what the 'end game' is likely to be all about?<br>
<br>
I'd appreciate any info really, the DAOC site still lacks detail on character descriptions, and the safehouse has thrown up a lot of conflicting thoughts on the classes.<br>
<br>
JayK 55 Monkey.<br>
<br>
<br>
